    "body": "Problem:\r\n:windo and :tabdo create an extra window when 'winfixbuf' is set.\r\n\r\nSolution:\r\nex_listdo() splits a new window to escape 'winfixbuf' so buffer-changing\r\ncommands can switch buffers. :windo and :tabdo don't change the current\r\nwindow's buffer, so skip that for them.\r\n\r\nCloses #40355 ",
